from jonesk subject re harry caray in article odell bernard write being an old time cardinal fan-now relocate to the nva area-i can recall that harry wa not at all popular with old man busch who a i understand it fire him and kick him out of st loui i be not quite sure of the reason but the old man wa certainly not enrapture by ole harry bern i grow up listen to harry carey call the cardinal game and really like him then but a i recall he wa fire because he wa too critical read honest when he wa announce he dare to point out the card miscue and such at least thi be what i remember from when i wa a kid kay jone 